{"tid":794349,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[身體最誠實] 譚耀宗：高鐵車程長過4個鐘一般考慮坐飛機","createTime":"2018-08-26T07:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T08:18:23.000Z","uid":136994,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad2f8a5c80bae38669f1a514033c986cece8dfe","tid":794349,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:25:07.000Z","msg":"廣深港高鐵香港段9月23日開通，全國人大常委譚耀宗指，不擔心高鐵效益，預計高鐵將受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n被問及會否搭高鐵北上「公幹」，包括赴北京開「兩會」等，譚耀宗稱視乎哪種交通工具較方便，「如果（車程）長過4個鐘頭，一般可能考慮坐飛機會多啲」。高鐵將設由香港開往北京的班次，車程需時約9小時。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗出席一個開幕活動後見記者，談及高鐵即將開通，他稱未來會有越來越多港人回內地，或更多內地人來港，預計高鐵受歡迎，不擔心效益和載客量。<br />\n<br />\n被問及日後若北上公幹，例如參加「兩會」時會否乘搭高鐵，譚耀宗指，要視乎哪種交通工具較方便，若天氣不好，乘飛機會遇阻濟，火車會較有保證。<br />\n<br />\n他補充，高鐵4小時內車程的班次會較多人選擇，「如果長過4個鐘頭，一般可能考慮坐飛機多啲」，但他認為，「如果你坐高鐵作為一種享受都可以，沿途你都睇到好多風光」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">譚耀宗居然唔支持偉大祖國嘅高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係其心可誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f8657c6723d61b9267f34e7d8bfeb8b759403032","tid":794349,"uid":15413,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/153709_c1a44b5eaea40fc74947aeb01b188649.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F153709_c1a44b5eaea40fc74947aeb01b188649.gif&h=8c39464f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"741504daade9c676b61b4d59d3b66440f348c549","tid":794349,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"賣完港，理得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87feede4daa3b27ebcfdf4ddde0f9ed61651a437","tid":794349,"uid":38666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/154141_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F154141_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d0539414&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25b0d284b80199ba5c06664c60c08652e3f12753","tid":794349,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"個缺口已經打開咗，有無人搭高鐵已經唔係最重要嘅問題"}]}